com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking.data

Class TrackerUserProfile.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking.data.TrackerUserProfile.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    TrackerUserProfile

    public static class TrackerUserProfile.Builder
extends Object
    This class builds a TrackerUserProfile instance with the user's height, weight, gender, and age.

       TrackerUserProfile profile = new TrackerUserProfile.Builder()
                   .setHeight(height)
                   .setWeight(weight)
                   .setGender(gender)
                   .setAge(age)
                   .build();

    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    HealthTrackerService.getHealthTracker(HealthTrackerType, TrackerUserProfile)
